description: Numbers n such that n! is not divisible by the square of (f+1)!, where f=Floor[n/2].
comments: Values of f are in A001057 or A004526.
example: 12 is here because 12!/(7!*7!)=132/7 is not an integer. 10 is not here because 10!/(6!*6!)=7 is an integer.
author: _Labos Elemer_, Jul 27 2000
